##########################
# GSEA+
##########################

(1) The downloaded directory (GSEAplus) contains all the files necessary for the correct execution of GSEA+.

# Scripts
- ui.R
- server.R
- GSEAfunctions.R
- app.R

# Report template
- gsea+report.Rmd

# Data files
- h.all.v7.5.1.symbols.gmt
- mart_export.txt

(2) GSEA+ is executed using R. The following libraries are necessary:

- library(ggplot2)
- library(shiny) 
- library(dplyr)
- library(shinydashboard)
- library(devtools)
- library(shinyFeedback)
- library(progress)
- library(rmarkdown) 
- library(knitr) 
- library(data.table)
- library(cowplot) 
- library(rintrojs) 
- library(shinyWidgets)

(3) GSEA+ can be run locally or using a browser.

# Local execution
- Use of Rstudio
- Run app.R file

# Browser distribution
- Use of the terminal
- Go to the working directory (cd GSEAplus)
- Execute: Rscript app.R
- If there were no errors a link were be displayed -> Listening on http://XXX.X.X.X:YYYY
- Open link


